transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Hi, thank you so much for calling Viagra at Score Blue.

Speaker 2: How can I help you today?

Speaker 1: Yes, sir, hi.

Speaker 2: I had a prescription that I canceled, and I sent back a vial. And Go-Go Med said they got it, but I haven't seen my refund yet.

Speaker 1: OK, let's take a look here and see what the holdup or the status is. Can I get the phone number associated with the account?

Speaker 2: 518-669-9499.

Speaker 1: Your full name and date of birth?

Speaker 2: Robert McCaffrey, 11-6-1956.

Speaker 1: OK, so I see here that we received it on the 20th. Go-Go Meds, rather. So that was issued on the 20th, and you might see it any day now, so either later today or tomorrow. But I see the refund was issued.

Speaker 2: OK, I checked my credit card yesterday, I think, or the day before. I don't know, it's been snowing so much here. I'll keep checking.

Speaker 1: Yeah, I do see it has been issued. Sometimes there can be small delays.

Speaker 2: Just depends on the credit institution. American Express, I've seen it next day, PayPal is immediate. But depending on the credit institution, it can usually take a little bit of time for it to go through.

Speaker 1: OK. Thank you very much.

Speaker 2: You're very welcome.

Speaker 1: Thank you.

Speaker 2: Have a good day.

Speaker 1: Bye-bye.

Speaker 2: Bye.
